nt/uploads/2023/08/Matty-Healy-performing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Matty-Healy-performing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Matty-Healy-performing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Matty-Healy-performing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Matty-Healy-performing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/the-1975">1975 年的</a>主唱马蒂·<a href="/artists/matty-healy">希利 (Matty Healy)</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/lollapalooza">2023 年 Lollapalooza 音乐</a>节的头条新闻中似乎嘲笑了乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-good-vibes-festival-malaysia-set-cut-short-matty-healy-criticises-anti-lgbtq-laws-kiss-bassist-3471738">目前在马来西亚的争议</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/every-lollapalooza-chicago-line-up-poster-3475808">自 1991 年以来的每一张 Lollapalooza 阵容海报</a></strong></li></ul><p>在他们的歌曲“It&#39;s Not Living If It&#39;s Not With You”的介绍中，乐队有一个笑话，希利说一些有争议的话，然后乐队用歌曲的开头即兴重复段打断了他。</p><p>在今年的音乐节上表演这首歌时，希利说：“你想要我的旅行小费吗？不要去……”，然后就被赛道的起点打断了。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cvi_1SkPvWs/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div